Notes

* Although Scikit-learn uses OLS and doesn't require normalization, it was applied for fair comparison.
* Pure Python is slower due to lack of vectorization.
* I used an LLM (ChatGPT) to figure out feature normalization when my model started diverging due to exploding gradients.

